Name: Lemon Blueberry Granola
Types: Rations
Components: Toasted Oats, Dried Blueberries, Lemon Zest
Description: This zesty, crunchy granola seems to never go stale and one bite is enough to fill the stomach of a grown man. When consumed, this ration helps give adventurers a boost when they thought they couldn't go on. Grants a number of temporary hit points equal to your Wisdom modifier + your Constitution modifier (minimum of 1).
